Type:
geo:AbstractMeasurementSourcePropertyType, complex content
Defined:
locally within geo:AbstractMeasurementType complexType
A reference to the source of the measurement. An example is a static GNSS baseline reduction from a pair of RINEX files via baseline processing software. Another example is atmospheric correction of a raw EDM measurement. Optional.
